level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All properties should be installed during the class initializer.  It"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"is possible to install properties after that, but doing so is not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"recommend, and specifically, is not guaranteed to be thread-safe vs."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"use of properties on the same type on other threads.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The property id of each property is the index of each "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpec","isActive":true},{"text":" in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pspecs"},{"type":"text","text":" array."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The property id of 0 is treated specially by "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","isActive":true},{"text":" and it should not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"be used to store a ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ParamSpec","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function should be used if you plan to use a static array of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GParamSpecs"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"text":". For instance, this","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"class initialization:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}]},{"syntax":"C","code":["typedef enum {","  PROP_FOO = 1,","  PROP_BAR,","  N_PROPERTIES","} MyObjectProperty;"